{"tid":1490522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明點解條片個9字係黑色既入","createTime":"2019-08-20T06:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T06:43:25.000Z","uid":201604,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e0398d2066f5bfca448fae34b669653e099ee5b7","tid":1490522,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:35:02.000Z","msg":"影白色淺色野就出黑字 影黑色深色野就出白字<br />\n<br />\nThe way that they do it is a dumb way to keep you always being able to see it.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cctvforum.com/images/imported/2014/05/246143_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cctvforum.com%2Fimages%2Fimported%2F2014%2F05%2F246143_1.jpg&h=ae03bc7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nFirst of all, it's kind of a stupid algorithm that changes it from black to white (or vice versa) when the background doesn't warrant it. It's also distracting when you are watching a live feed or a video and looking for the motion and keep noticing the changing colors of the time stamp. And it's just ugly when it isn't uniform.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cctvforum.com/topic/37157-why-does-hikvision-change-the-timestamp-from-black-to-white/#comment-237872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cctvforum.com%2Ftopic%2F37157-why-does-hikvision-change-the-timestamp-from-black-to-white%2F%23comment-237872&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VuSwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=17608ead\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cctvforum.com/topic/37157-why-does-hikvision-change-the-timestamp-from-black-to-white/#comment-237872</a>"},{"pid":"ef33ac72a5ee9f2ea3e381d66650f9f52ddc9599","tid":1490522,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:37:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d55c3e3a5473204f67b72f2f26d394eefa20b8d1","tid":1490522,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:38:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a314fad7d486dc890c0b956fb7b120462f8db93","tid":1490522,"uid":85926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e4fac81ac23f018c0b77554b88d0556135b0b4","tid":1490522,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:43:25.000Z","msg":"班藍絲唔會理你架<br />\n佢地就好似森美所講個堆支持地平說既人一樣<br />\n「唔係喎，有片影到地球係圓架喎」<br />\n「條片假既！啲片係偽造既！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}